title: Arkansas State's Brown is Sun Belt Defensive Player of Week
text:
Arkansas State’s Brown is Sun Belt Defensive Player of Week By - Associated Press   
JONESBORO, Ark. (AP) - Arkansas State defensive back Cody Brown has been named the Sun Belt Conference Defensive Player of the Week. 
Brown was announced Monday as the winner of the award following is play in the Red Wolves’ win on Thursday over Louisiana-Lafayette. 
Brown’s night included an interception that he returned 30 yards for a touchdown in Arkansas State’s 37-27 win.
